iness%20Insider%20about%20her%20loved%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20began%20as%20a%20personal%20tool%20to%20vent%2C%20think%20through%20decisions%2C%20and%20avoid%20snapping%20at%20her%20five-year-old%20son%20after%20a%20long%20workday%20soon%20became%20something%20bigger%3A%20Crash%20Out%20Diary%2C%20a%20web%20app%20for%20emotional%20offloading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20account%20director%20at%20a%20marketing%20agency%20vibe-coded%20the%20app%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20help%20people%20regulate%20their%20emotions.%20The%20free%20app%20is%20anonymous%20and%20doesn't%20save%20messages%20unless%20users%20create%20an%20account%2C%20Williams%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20typical%20chatbots%2C%20Crash%20Out%20Diary%20focuses%20on%20a%20single%20interaction.%20Users%20send%20one%20message%2C%20receive%20a%20short%20pep%20talk%2C%20and%20are%20guided%20to%20an%20activity%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20a%20tapping%20game%20or%20a%20breathing%20exercise%20%E2%80%94%20to%20help%20them%20feel%20more%20grounded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams%20said%20%26quot%3Bcrashing%20out%26quot%3B%20is%20akin%20to%20emotionally%20unraveling%3A%20%26quot%3BYou're%20dealing%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20stuff%20at%20one%20time%20and%20you're%20having%20an%20external%20reaction%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20posted%20a%20video%20about%20the%20web%20app%20on%20social%20media%2C%20where%20it%20hit%202%20million%20views%20on%20Instagram.%20Since%20its%20April%20launch%2C%20the%20app%20has%20hosted%20about%2050%2C000%20%26quot%3Bcrash%20out%20sessions%2C%26quot%3B%20Williams%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2257a0911b-5990-4ded-ab8d-9c4c488a5824%5C%22%3EAI%20supports%20her%20in%20ways%20friends%20can't%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams%20first%20turned%20to%20Claude%20to%20help%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-therapy-risks-benefits-boundaries-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprocess%20emotions%3C%2Fa%3E%20she%20didn't%20feel%20comfortable%20sharing.%20She%20was%20juggling%20work%20stress%20and%20anger%20at%20a%20former%20boss%2C%20so%20she%20built%20a%20private%20project%20in%20Claude%20using%20notes%20from%20her%20life%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe'd%20go%20to%20the%20AI%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BOk%2C%20how%20do%20we%20calm%20myself%20down%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20be%20regulated%20at%20work.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20show%20up%20angry%20or%20mad%2C%26quot%3B%20she%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etold%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClaude's%20tone%20was%20unexpectedly%20warm.%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20seen%20by%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20really%20helped%20her%20was%20the%20AI's%20ability%20to%20organize%20her%20thinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20worried%20about%20a%20client%20issue%2C%20and%20I%20was%20like%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20I'm%20going%20to%20see%20through%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20Claude%20talked%20me%20through%20it%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20got%20this.%20You%20just%20need%20to%20do%20X%2C%20Y%2C%20and%20Z%20%E2%80%94%20you%20already%20have%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20kind%20of%20clarity%20was%20something%20she%20didn't%20always%20get%20from%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20help%20%26quot%3Buntangle%20your%20thought%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20friends%20can't%20do%20for%20you%2C%20or%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20put%20onto%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20found%20comfort%20in%20AI's%20on-demand%20nature.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20inappropriate%20time%20to%20talk%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20I'm%20telling%20the%20same%20story%20over%20and%20over%20to%20my%20friends%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20like%20my%20friends%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20there.%20It's%20just%20that%20sometimes%20I%20need%20a%20different%20perspective.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223072a16c-e910-49ae-8cb5-211513559222%5C%22%3EAI%20has%20made%20her%20a%20more%20present%20mom%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams%20said%20using%20AI%20has%20also%20made%20her%20a%20better%20parent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20helps%20her%20not%20spiral%20into%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20a%20good%20mom%26quot%3B%20thoughts%2C%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20shows%20me%20the%20things%20that%20I%20do%20well%20about%20being%20a%20mom.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20long%20workdays%2C%20Williams%20often%20feels%20drained%20%E2%80%94%20but%20her%20five-year-old%20still%20wants%20her%20full%20attention.%20Talking%20to%20AI%20became%20her%20reset%20button%2C%20helping%20her%20decompress%20before%20stepping%20into%20mom%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20better%20mom%20because%20I'm%20not%20so%20wound%20up%20and%20stressed%2C%20so%20I%20can%20really%20pay%20attention%20to%20my%20son%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams%20uses%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-kids-never-smarter-than-ai-chatgpt-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20in%20everyday%20parenting%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20she%20and%20her%20son%20found%20bugs%20in%20the%20house%2C%20they%20snapped%20photos%2C%20fed%20them%20into%20an%20AI%20tool%2C%20and%20identified%20them%20together.%20On%20nature%20walks%2C%20they%20use%20AI%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20names%20of%20plants%20and%20animals%20they%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20helps%20me%20be%20more%20informative%20with%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225b7c218f-293c-4177-81ce-b22b6fcfe7ea%5C%22%3EShe%20asks%20AI%20to%20talk%20to%20her%20like%20she%20was%2010%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Williams%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-vibe-code-app-cynthia-chen-prompting-ai-designer-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20the%20web%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20didn't%20know%20how%20to%20structure%20a%20product%2C%20let%20al