0don't%20think%20this%20is%20on%20people's%20radar%2C%26quot%3B%20Amodei%20later%20told%20Axios.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReichstadter%20is%20asking%20Amodei%20to%20stop%20frontier%20development%20altogether.%20He%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20phone%20interview%20that%20he%20delivered%20a%20letter%20to%20Amodei's%20desk%20on%20his%20first%20day%20of%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20that%20letter%2C%20I%20asked%20him%20to%20stop%20developing%20that%20technology%20and%20to%20do%20everything%20in%20his%20power%20to%20stop%20the%20race%20that%20he's%20participating%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20told%20him%20I'd%20be%20out%20here%20in%20front%20of%20his%20office%20waiting%20for%20his%20answer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20then%2C%20he%20said%20he'll%20subsist%20on%20water%2C%20electrolytes%2C%20and%20multivitamins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20concrete%20world%20in%20which%20we're%20living%20right%20now%2C%20all%20of%20the%20frontier%20labs%20are%20racing%20as%20quickly%20as%20they%20can%20to%20fully%20general%20superhuman%20systems.%20That's%20what%20needs%20to%20stop%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20great%20things%20could%20be%20done%20with%20very%20limited%20systems%20that%20don't%20pose%20the%20same%20kinds%20of%20risks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReichstadter%20said%20in%202022%20he%20went%20on%20a%2015-day%20strike%20without%20food%20outside%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Miami%20mayor%20to%20draw%20attention%20to%20the%20climate%20crisis%2C%20and%20felt%20like%20he%20could%20have%20kept%20going.%20He%20said%20he%20was%20so%20far%20%26quot%3Bfeeling%20good%26quot%3B%20this%20time%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReichstadter%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20Stop%20AI%2C%20a%20group%20that%20describes%20itself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bnon-violent%20civil%20resistance%20organization%20working%20to%20permanently%20ban%20the%20development%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-talent-war-superintel