South%20Korea's%20leaders%20are%20now%20scrambling%20to%20contain%20the%20fallout%20both%20at%20home%20and%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGi-Wook%20Shin%2C%20a%20sociology%20professor%20and%20founding%20director%20of%20Stanford%20University's%20Korean%20Studies%20Program%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20raid%20puts%20South%20Korean%20President%20Lee%20Jae%20Myung%20in%20a%20difficult%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Korean%20leader%20needs%20to%20balance%20the%20country's%20alliance%20overseas%20with%20his%20nation's%20own%20interests%2C%20he%20said.%20Back%20home%2C%20Lee%20faces%20his%20liberal%20supporters%20who%2C%20while%20not%20enthusiastic%20about%20Trump%2C%20nonetheless%20accept%20that%20the%20country%20needs%20to%20work%20with%20the%20US%2C%20Shin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Lee%20Government%20is%20really%20trying%20to%20work%20with%20the%20Trump%20administration%20to%20strengthen%20the%20alliance%20and%20really%20trying%20to%20accommodate%20Trump's%20policy%2C%26quot%3B%20Shin%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20that's%20why%20what%20happened%20now%20is%20not%20good%20timing%2C%20and%20Mr.%20Lee%20will%20be%20in%20a%20tough%20position%20politically%20inside%20Korea.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20months%2C%20South%20Korean%20officials%20have%20met%20with%20the%20Trump%20administration%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-auto-tariffs-rattle-markets-carmakers-parts-thailand-china-reallocation-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrade%20talks%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20announced%20massive%20investments%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Lee's%20August%20summit%20at%20the%20White%20House%2C%20South%20Korea%20unveiled%20a%20%24150%20billion%20investment%20into%20the%20US%2C%20backed%20by%20private%20companies.%20Hyundai%20Motor%20Group%20alone%20announced%20a%20%2426%20billion%20pledge%20%E2%80%94%20part%20of%20which%20would%20go%20toward%20a%20new%20steel%20mill%20plant%20in%20Louisiana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhyundai-metaplant-georgia-us-ev-factory-tour-photos-see-inside-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHyundai%20factory%3C%2Fa%3E%20raided%20on%20Thursday%20in%20Ellabell%2C%20Georgia%20%E2%80%94%20about%2030%20miles%20west%20of%20Savannah%20%E2%80%94%20is%20the%20company's%20largest%20manufacturing%20footprint%20in%20the%20South.%20The%20facility%20had%20its%20grand%20opening%20in%20late%20March%20with%20an%20event%20that%20was%20attended%20by%20Republican%20Gov.%20Brian%20Kemp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20joint%20investment%20from%20LG%20Energy%20Solutions%2C%20the%20so-called%20Metaplant%20grew%20into%20a%20%247.59%20billion%20investment%2C%20projected%20to%20bring%20in%208%2C500%20jobs%20to%20the%20state.%20Parts%20of%20the%203%2C000-acre%20campus%20were%20still%20under%20construction%20during%20the%20raid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20LG%20Energy%20Solutions%20said%20about%20250%20affected%20workers%20were%20affiliated%20with%20the%20HL-GA%20Battery%20Company%2C%20a%20joint%20venture%20between%20Hyundai%20Motor%20Group%20and%20LG%20Energy%20Solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20now%2C%20our%20top%20priority%20is%20ensuring%20the%20safety%20and%20well-being%20of%20our%20employees%20and%20partners%2C%20and%20we%20will%20commit%20our%20best%20efforts%20to%20ensure%20their%20safe%20and%20prompt%20returns%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20for%20comment%2C%20Hyundai%20Motor%20Group%20referred%20Business%20Insider%20to%20its%20statement%20released%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20reviewing%20our%20processes%20to%20ensure%20that%20all%20parties%20working%20on%20our%20projects%20maintain%20the%20same%20high%20standards%20of%20legal%20compliance%20that%20we%20demand%20of%20ourselves%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20includes%20thorough%20vetting%20of%20employment%20practices%20by%20contractors%20and%20subcontractors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA.J.%20Jacobs%2C%20an%20East%20Carolina%20University%20professor%20who%20has%20written%20two%20volumes%20on%20the%20Korean%20automotive%20industry%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Hyundai%20has%20so%20far%20supported%20nearly%2030%2C000%20direct%20and%20indirect%20jobs%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHyundai's%20first%20major%20US%20plant%20was%20completed%20in%20Montgomery%2C%20Alabama%2C%20in%202005.%20In%202009%2C%20the%20Korean%20automaker%20opened%20another%20plant%20about%2090%20miles%20away%20in%20West%20Point%2C%20Georgia%2C%20bringing%20in%20another%203%2C200%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20investments%20came%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20regions%20were%20seeing%20high%20unemployment%20rates%20and%20industrial%20decline%2C%20Jacobs%20said.%20Alabama%20and%20Georgia%20weren't%20yet%20the%20major%20auto%20manufacturing%20centers%20they%20are%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20it's%20done%20is%20it%20brought%20prestige%20to%20their%20governors%20and%20mayors%2C%20got%20them%20re-elected%2C%20and%20it's%20brought%20some%20visibility%20to%20those%20states%20for%20international%20investors%20and%20foreign%20direct%20investment%2C%26quot%3B%20Jacobs%20said.%20%26quot%3BTo%20quantify%20the%20impact%20of%20these%20investments%20%E2%80%94%20I%20really%20couldn't%20even%20venture%20to%20guess%20how%20many%20billions%20of%20dollars%20have%20been%20invested%20in%20Alabama%20and%20Georgia%20prior%20to%20the%20Metaplant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20its%20deep%20roots%20in%20the%20South%2C%20Jacobs%20said%20there's%20little%20that%20would%20push%20Hyundai%20to%20abandon%20its%20production%20centers%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20my%20opinion%2C%20there's%20almost%20nothing%20that%20would%20get%20them%20to%20stop%20producing%20vehicles%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20stop%20growing%2C%26quot%3B%20Jacobs%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20hit%20an%20all-time%20sales%20record%20again%20this%20month.%20Every%20year%20they%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShin%2C%20the%20Stanford%20professor%2C%20said%20South%20Korea%20will%20likely%20be%20cautious%20in%20its%20response%2C%20especially%20if%20the%20probe%20unveils%20that%20any%20of%20the%20detainees%20were%20breaking%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%20morning%2C%20multiple%20Korean%20media%20reported%20that%20the%20president's%20chief%20of%20staff%2C%20Kang%20Hoon-Sik%2C%20announced%20a%20deal%20to%20release%20more%20than%20300%20South%20Korean%20workers%20detained%20in%20the%20raid.%20The%20official%20said%20a%20charter%20plane%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20bring%20the%20workers%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20criminal%20charges%20have%20been%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhite%20House%20spokesperson%20Abigail%20Jackson%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3BTrump%20will%20continue%20delivering%20on%20his%20promise%20to%20make%20the%20United%20States%20the%20best%20place%20in%20the%20world%20to%20do%20business%2C%20while%20also%20enforcing%20federal%20immigration%20laws.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhyundai-ice-raid-us-south-korea-auto-manufacturing-investment-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757264149000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68bd8f56f9db348adc0afefd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhyundai-ice-raid-us-south-korea-auto-manufacturing-investment-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ICE%20raid%20on%20a%20Hyundai%20plant%2C%20one%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Blargest%26quot%3B%20in%20history%2C%20is%20reverberating%20far%20beyond%20the%20rural%20Georgia%20town%20where%20it%20took%20place.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A428%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.c