p%3EI've%20been%20to%20dozens%20of%20weddings%20in%20different%20places%2C%20from%20backyards%20and%20churches%20to%20high-end%20homestead%20hotels%20and%20wineries.%20I%20once%20even%20attended%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdouble-zoo-wedding-proposal-video-2018-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewedding%20at%20a%20zoo%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20another%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20a%20museum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20no%20matter%20the%20type%20of%20celebration%20%E2%80%94%20casual%2C%20fancy%2C%20or%20in-between%20%E2%80%94%20I%20have%20seen%20and%20heard%20firsthand%20what%20matters%20most%20to%20guests.%20No%2C%20it's%20not%20the%20favors%20or%20the%20cake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20throw%20a%20wedding%20that%20guests%20will%20rave%20about%20for%20years%2C%20here%20are%20three%20things%20you%20need%20to%20focus%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22618dd322-10a9-40ea-9a41-745b3a886ad5%5C%22%3EGuests%20expect%20a%20good%20meal%20(and%20decent%20portions%20of%20it)%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20Tegan%20Forder%20smiling%20with%20man%20in%20suit%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b847a0a17a8c5b4053e99c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20often%20remember%20the%20weddings%20where%20we%20left%20hungry%20or%20feeling%20incredibly%20satisfied.%3Cp%3ETegan%20Forder%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20wedding%2C%20I%20was%20served%20a%20sausage%20in%20a%20piece%20of%20bread.%20The%20meagre%20offering%20was%20slightly%20offset%20by%20the%20venue's%20stunning%20views%20of%20the%20sunset%2C%20but%20it%20still%20sticks%20in%20my%20mind%20as%20not%20being%20quite%20what%20was%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20guest%20will%20remember%20if%20they%20need%20to%20stop%20on%20the%20way%20home%20for%20a%20fast-food%20top-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20unofficial%20contract%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-wedding-guests-should-never-make-etiquette-coach-tips%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebeing%20a%20wedding%20guest%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you%20expect%20a%20decent%20meal%20in%20exchange%20for%20your%20investment%20(paying%20to%20get%20there%2C%20giving%20a%20gift%2C%20maybe%20even%20buying%20a%20new%20outfit%2C%20or%20booking%20a%20hotel).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20weddings%20with%20just%20a%20cocktail%20menu%20can%20be%20tricky%20to%20nail%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20often%20never%20enough%20food%2C%20and%20where%20you%20stand%20will%20dictate%20how%20often%20the%20waitstaff%20come%20your%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20my%20experience%2C%20shared%20platters%20are%20a%20solid%20approach%20if%20you%20want%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-making-wedding-look-cheap-luxury-planner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eelevate%20a%20wedding%20meal%3C%2Fa%3E%20beyond%20a%20buffet%20or%20the%20choice%20between%20plated%20chicken%20or%20steak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20plates%20of%20meat%2C%20salads%2C%20and%20sides%20are%20distributed%20at%20each%20table%20for%20everyone%20to%20help%20themselves.%20That%20way%2C%20guests%20have%20some%20choice%20in%20what%20they%20eat%20and%20how%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222ab66299-7e4b-402f-bfc1-7c41523492aa%5C%22%3EIt's%20crucial%20to%20have%20a%20dance%20floor%20that%20keeps%20the%20party%20going%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20couple%2C%20the%20wedding%20day%20is%20about%20celebrating%20their%20relationship%20in%20front%20of%20loved%20ones%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-remember-everything-2016-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecreating%20special%20memories%3C%2Fa%3E%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20guests%2C%20it's%20about%20getting%20dressed%20up%2C%20catching%20up%20with%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20and%20having%20a%20party.%20This%20means%20you%20need%20to%20nail%20some%20good%20music%20for%20the%20dance%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20live%20band%20can%20be%20great%2C%20but%20only%20if%20they're%20given%20a%20clear%20guide%20on%20what%20songs%20to%20play%20and%20especially%20what%20not%20to.%20I've%20been%20to%20several%20weddings%20where%20the%20song%20choices%20have%20been%20downright%20boring%2C%20resulting%20in%20deserted%20dance%20floors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20putting%20together%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsongs-celebrities-play-at-their-weddings-ones-they-skip-dj%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewedding%20playlist%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20keep%20the%20slower%20songs%20for%20earlier%20on%20in%20the%20night%20and%20be%20sure%20to%20up%20the%20tempo%20as%20the%20reception%20progresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-unique-ideas-weddings-from-expert-planner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20weddings%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20when%20the%20couple%20puts%20their%20own%20stamp%20on%20the%20music%20(without%20offending%20grandma)%20while%20including%20enough%20wedding%20anthems%20that%20everyone%20will%20leave%20their%20seats%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f42518e8-6015-4aae-a150-e67cd09c18a8%5C%22%3EShoot%20for%20speeches%20that%20are%20memorable%20for%20the%20right%20reasons%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20Tegan%20Forder%20posing%20with%20man%20in%20blazer%20in%20front%20of%20green%20hills%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b847a0a17a8c5b4053e99b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20love%20a%20speech%20that's%20short%20and%20sweet.%3Cp%3ETegan%20Forder%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWedding%20speeches%20can%20be%20funny%2C%20witty%2C%20and%20poignant.%20They%20can%20also%20be%20too%20long%2C%20boring%2C%20and%20cringeworthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKeep%20the%20speeches%20short%20and%20limit%20who%20