%20am%20internally%20motivated%20today%2C%20nobody%20is%20pushing%20me.%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20doing%20it%20for%20fame%2C%20money%20or%20external%20validation.%20I%E2%80%99m%20doing%20it%20because%20I%20love%20doing%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarpreet%20points%20out%20that%20we%20need%20to%20teach%20children%20to%20regulate%20their%20emotions.%20Hitting%20obviously%20is%20not%20the%20right%20way%20to%20do%20it%2C%20nor%20is%20propping%20them%20up%20before%20a%20screen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20they%20are%2030%20and%20angry%2C%20are%20they%20going%20to%20see%20a%20screen%20and%20pacify%20themselves%3F%20We%20should%20not%20teach%20children%20to%20distract%20themselves%20because%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20help%20them%20process%20their%20emotions.%20Just%20because%20we%20weren%E2%80%99t%20taught%20this%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20we%20should%20repeat%20it%20with%20the%20next%20generation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20child%20is%20watching%20a%20screen%2C%20they%20are%20not%20involved%20in%20anything%20around%20them.%20That%20is%20the%20core%20issue%20which%20leads%20to%20many%20mental%20health%20problems.%20To%20prevent%20this%2C%20we%20need%20to%20involve%20children%20in%20a%20daily%20routine%20doing%20household%20chores%2C%20take%20them%20outside%2C%20and%20build%20a%20community%20of%20friends%20for%20them%20to%20play%20with.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20keep%20children%20involved%20in%20purposeful%20work%20which%20also%20fosters%20empathy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-32-1724422779.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-webs